title: 214: SIX Things to Stop Doing in 2021
description:
What are some of the things we can stop doing to win in 2021?

We all have a to-do list, but I think it is even more important to have a not-to-do list. More often than not, many of us fill our schedules and lives with the very things that are diminishing our peace of mind, profitability, productivity, positivity, and performance.

In this episode, I share the importance of letting go of the things that hold you back and weigh you down. I believe you are meant to soar, and by removing some of those unconscious behaviors and patterns, your life can become limitless. 

If you are ready to advance beyond what you ever thought was possible and win in 2021, this episode is for you.
